<p><span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">另外G8003次变更沈阳北站终到</span></strong></span></p>
<p><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">大连火车站提醒广大旅客</span></strong></p>
<p><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">有关列车停运及正晚点动态</span></strong></p>
